{"tid":2132531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8人坐艇往西貢火石洲　外籍男攀石墮海亡　6人被困岩石","createTime":"2020-07-30T12:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T14:04:43.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"01b7a6cfde7a39a3590b63f6331d5fef00b94232","tid":2132531,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:22:34.000Z","msg":"8人坐艇往西貢火石洲 外籍男攀石墮海亡 6人被困岩石<br />\n2020-07-30 16:33<br />\n<br />\n&quot;今日（30日）下午約2時半，警方及消防接獲報案稱，有6名人士於火石洲對開海面懷疑被困於岩石上，警方及消防接報後趕往現場，政府飛行服務隊亦出動救援。初步消息指，事件原涉及8人，包括兩名外籍男子及一個6人家庭，8人坐艇出海前往火石洲，其後兩名男子於攀石期間墮海，一名男子懷疑遇溺昏迷，需要施行心肺復蘇法，由直升機送往東區醫院搶救，惜證實不治。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/504746/8%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%90%E8%89%87%E5%BE%80%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E7%81%AB%E7%9F%B3%E6%B4%B2-%E5%A4%96%E7%B1%8D%E7%94%B7%E6%94%80%E7%9F%B3%E5%A2%AE%E6%B5%B7%E4%BA%A1-6%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E5%9B%B0%E5%B2%A9%E7%9F%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F504746%2F8%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%259D%2590%25E8%2589%2587%25E5%25BE%2580%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25B2%25A2%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%259F%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%25B1%258D%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%2594%2580%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E4%25BA%25A1-6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259B%25B0%25E5%25B2%25A9%25E7%259F%25B3&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=bbd22570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/504746/8%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%90%E8%89%87%E5%BE%80%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E7%81%AB%E7%9F%B3%E6%B4%B2-%E5%A4%96%E7%B1%8D%E7%94%B7%E6%94%80%E7%9F%B3%E5%A2%AE%E6%B5%B7%E4%BA%A1-6%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E5%9B%B0%E5%B2%A9%E7%9F%B3</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">RIP</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e75ce5889eaebd99f4d0f8aa83057a1174b6e4d2","tid":2132531,"uid":79793,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:27:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母肺炎仲出去玩 抵死啦柒頭"},{"pid":"2a8165ff7